      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCOOTIN' SCOOBY (8) slotted in just off the lead from the wide box before lifting strongly to score (19.95) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 340m. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Looks the one to beat. WALK THE TALK (1) ran below his best last time finishing fourth (19.96) over 340m at this track in a NG. Form here sound including eight wins. The form from his last run stacks up well. Has the ability to give this a shake. ZIPPING SCHRUB (2) goes very well this trip starting 13 times for seven wins and three minors. Placed last time (23.20) at The Gardens in a Free For All, finishing third and beaten 4 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. MY MACHINE (7) clocked a strong 19.73 despite finishing fourth last start. Can measure up here.",
